{
  "stem": "232.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were eating whatever came in the-- people were-- it's known that people were eating pieces of other people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The hunger was this big.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "One-- one day, one morning, we heard a very, very funny noise, like-- like a million of chains rattling.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And-- and it came closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the soldiers were gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "All of a sudden, there was no more guards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And here, the British unit-- [CRYING] British army liberated us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[CRYING] This was on April 15, 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were free.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We-- we were that free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We didn't know where to turn, no family, nobody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And after a few days, different commissions came from different countries.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We had-- from all over the world, people from Greece, from France, from-- from Germany, Poland, all inmates.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And, of course, the-- the people from France and Belgium took their people right away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They didn't want them to linger around in it camp there, in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So I talked pretty well French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Papers we didn't have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I just said the number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I went to the French commission and said, I am French-born on the border from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And my name-- I gave my real name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I said, I am French citizen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I would like to go back home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So they considered me as a Frenchman, and I got a-- a paper showing that I'm French.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And two days later, my name was called out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And all the French people were sent on trucks to-- to France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The food we got was-- we got in the morning a-- a portion of bread, a little piece like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-called tea or coffee, something black to drink.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at night, when we came back, we got a soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
